This product includes software developed in the Hermax project and integrates
bindings and wrappers around third-party MaxSAT/SAT solvers with their own
licenses and citation requirements.

Citation request
----------------
If you use Hermax in research, please cite:

- Repository: https://github.com/josalhor/hermax

and cite relevant solver/paper references for the evaluated backend(s).

